{"id":14239,"date":"2023-03-18T16:54:01","date_gmt":"2023-03-18T09:54:01","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/?p=14239"},"modified":"2023-03-18T16:54:01","modified_gmt":"2023-03-18T09:54:01","slug":"hyundai-dung-thu-ba-the-gioi-ve-san-xuat-o-to","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/hyundai-dung-thu-ba-the-gioi-ve-san-xuat-o-to\/","title":{"rendered":"Hyundai \u0111\u1ee9ng th\u1ee9 ba th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi v\u1ec1 s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t \u00f4 t\u00f4"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>Th\u00f4ng t\u1ea5n Yonhap ng\u00e0y 15\/3\/2023 \u0111\u01b0a tin, v\u1edbi s\u1ea3n l\u01b0\u1ee3ng b\u00e1n h\u00e0ng n\u0103m 2022 \u0111\u1ea1t 6,85 tri\u1ec7u xe, Hyundai (bao g\u1ed3m th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u con Kia) tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh nh\u00e0 s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t \u00f4 t\u00f4 l\u1edbn th\u1ee9 ba th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi.<\/p>\n<div>\n<p class=\"image\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"width100 initial loaded aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.baogiaothong.vn\/upload\/images\/2023-1\/article_img\/2023-03-15\/img-bgt-2021-screenshot-364--1678893506-width1280height720.jpg\" alt=\"hyundai \u0111\u1ee9ng th\u1ee9 ba th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi v\u1ec1 s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t \u00f4 t\u00f4\" data-original=\"https:\/\/cdn.baogiaothong.vn\/upload\/images\/2023-1\/article_img\/2023-03-15\/img-bgt-2021-screenshot-364--1678893506-width1280height720.jpg\" data-was-processed=\"true\" \/><\/p>\n<p class=\"img_chu_thich\">Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch T\u1eadp \u0111o\u00e0n \u00f4 t\u00f4 Hyundai Euisun Chung t\u1ea1i s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n khai tr\u01b0\u01a1ng nh\u00e0 m\u00e1y \u1edf M\u1ef9 n\u0103m 2022<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<p>Toyota \u0111\u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi 10,5 tri\u1ec7u chi\u1ebfc v\u00e0 Volkswagen \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 hai v\u1edbi 8,5 tri\u1ec7u xe \u0111\u00e3 b\u00e1n.<\/p>\n<p>\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean doanh s\u1ed1 b\u00e1n h\u00e0ng k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p c\u1ee7a Hyundai Motor v\u00e0 Kia l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o top 3 tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng to\u00e0n c\u1ea7u sau 47 n\u0103m k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi Hyundai s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t chi\u1ebfc xe \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, mang t\u00ean Pony.<\/p>\n<p>Hyundai v\u00e0 Kia \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Li\u00ean minh Renault &#8211; Nissan &#8211; Mitsubishi (b\u00e1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 6,16 tri\u1ec7u xe) v\u00e0 General Motors (b\u00e1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 5,84 tri\u1ec7u xe).<\/p>\n<p>Trong s\u1ed1 6 nh\u00e0 s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t \u00f4 t\u00f4 l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t, g\u1ed3m Toyota, Volkswagen, Hyundai, Li\u00ean minh Renault &#8211; Nissan &#8211; Mitsubishi, General Motors, Stellantis, duy nh\u1ea5t Hyundai c\u00f3 s\u1ed1 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng xe b\u00e1n ra t\u0103ng 2,7% so v\u1edbi n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc (2021).<\/p>\n<p>Doanh s\u1ed1 c\u1ee7a Li\u00ean minh Renault &#8211; Nissan &#8211; Mitsubishi \u0111\u00e3 gi\u1ea3m 14,1% trong khi doanh s\u1ed1 c\u1ee7a Stellantis gi\u1ea3m 11,2%.<\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<div class=\"relatedNewsBellow\">\n<div class=\"relatedNewsBellowInner\">\n<div class=\"eventBox padB10 padT10\">\n<div class=\"eventBoxImg eventBoxLeft\"><a title=\"img\" href=\"https:\/\/xe.baogiaothong.vn\/doanh-so-xe-hyundai-tang-gan-60-bat-chap-thi-truong-lao-doc-d584469.html\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"width100 loaded aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.baogiaothong.vn\/upload\/images\/2023-1\/article_avatar_img\/2023-03-13\/img-bgt-2021-hyundai-accent-2021-2-1678676974-width1280height720.jpeg\" alt=\"hyundai \u0111\u1ee9ng th\u1ee9 ba th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi v\u1ec1 s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t \u00f4 t\u00f4\" data-original=\"https:\/\/cdn.baogiaothong.vn\/upload\/images\/2023-1\/article_avatar_img\/2023-03-13\/img-bgt-2021-hyundai-accent-2021-2-1678676974-width1280height720.jpeg\" data-was-processed=\"true\" \/><\/a><\/div>\n<div class=\"eventBoxRight\">\n<div class=\"marT05 sapo color-title\">\n<h4 class=\"bold\">Doanh s\u1ed1 xe Hyundai t\u0103ng g\u1ea7n 60% b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng lao d\u1ed1c<\/h4>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<p>Nh\u00e0 s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t \u00f4 t\u00f4 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u00e3 \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 n\u0103m th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi v\u1ec1 doanh s\u1ed1 trong h\u01a1n m\u1ed9t th\u1eadp k\u1ef7 k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb n\u0103m 2010, khi l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Ford.<\/p>\n<p>Sau \u0111\u00f3 Hyundai th\u0103ng h\u1ea1ng l\u00ean v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 t\u01b0 v\u00e0o n\u0103m 2020 nh\u01b0ng t\u1ee5t xu\u1ed1ng th\u1ee9 n\u0103m v\u00e0o n\u0103m 2021.<\/p>\n<p>Hi\u1ec7u su\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd ph\u1ea7n l\u1edbn l\u00e0 do doanh s\u1ed1 b\u00e1n h\u00e0ng \u1edf n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 xe Genesis cao c\u1ea5p v\u00e0 xe th\u00e2n thi\u1ec7n v\u1edbi m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng.<\/p>\n<p>T\u1ed5ng th\u1ecb ph\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a Hyundai v\u00e0 Kia \u0111\u1ea1t 10,8% t\u1ea1i th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng M\u1ef9 v\u00e0o n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i v\u00e0 9,4% t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u \u00c2u, c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea1t m\u1ee9c cao k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c.<\/p>\n<p>Hyundai v\u00e0 Kia \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau b\u00e1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 7,52 tri\u1ec7u xe trong n\u0103m 2023, t\u0103ng 9,6% so v\u1edbi n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Th\u00f4ng t\u1ea5n Yonhap ng\u00e0y 15\/3\/2023 \u0111\u01b0a tin, v\u1edbi s\u1ea3n l\u01b0\u1ee3ng b\u00e1n h\u00e0ng n\u0103m 2022 \u0111\u1ea1t 6,85 tri\u1ec7u xe, Hyundai (bao g\u1ed3m th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u con Kia) tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh nh\u00e0 s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t \u00f4 t\u00f4 l\u1edbn th\u1ee9 ba th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch T\u1eadp \u0111o\u00e0n \u00f4 t\u00f4 Hyundai Euisun Chung t\u1ea1i s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n khai tr\u01b0\u01a1ng nh\u00e0 m\u00e1y \u1edf M\u1ef9 [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""}